PrecisAppointment of Susan Bincoletto as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Swiss Confederation; Louise Blais as Ambassador and Deputy Permanent Representative of Canada to the United Nations, in New York; René Cremonese as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Zimbabwe; Emmanuelle Lamoureux as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Lebanese Republic; Nathalie O’Neil as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of Cameroon; and Julie Shouldice as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Côte d’Ivoire.
